The paper deals with the problem of link and node delay estimation in networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses compressive sensing algorithms, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of algorithms and computational complexity analysis, which are topics related to computer science theory (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with network tomography, which is a topic related to control and systems engineering (cs.SY).
